@realmoney Nov 23, 2020 | 01:15 PM EST DOUG KASS I Would No Longer Chase Value * Given the dominant absolute and relative performance of late The pivot from growth to value has been underscored by the price action over the last month, last week, and today. There is now

little doubt of the pivot - an idea which was met by a lot of criticism a few months ago. Indeed, some of the loudest critics are now buyers of value and sellers of growth - which was as predictable as the sun setting tonight in a market dominated by reactionary price chasers.
